
Quick startup/demo
1. Run ./simuinio
2. Type load
3. Type run
4. Press h to see options
5. Press R to run first loop
6. Press r continuously to iterate through loops

Updating the Board code
1. Edit BurnerBoardv2.ino
2. Go to step 1 above


Updating from another code
1. Copy the .ino file from Ardunio into this directory
2. Add this line near the start of your file
// BOARD_TYPE   MEGA
3. Create a .conf file like bb.conf with your project name.conf
4. ./simuino
5. Type list
6. Select your .conf by number
7. Goto step 2 at top
(if Err shows, type err to see the errors in your .ino code)


